<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>make light of something • make light work of something</xh5><p> <i>make light of something—</i>treat smth. as unimportant: My parents <u>made light of</u> my worry and told me to take no notice of what people said.</p><p> <i>make light work of something—</i>do smth. easily and without much effort: You have worked hard all year, and should be able to <u>make light work of</u> passing the examinations.</p> </entry>
